<title>USA: Western Springs, Ill. won by Bernardi Sec.</title>
<headline>Western Springs, Ill. won by Bernardi Sec.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bernardi Securities, Inc., said it won $1.900 million of Western Springs, Ill., general obligation bonds, Series 1997, with a net interest cost of 5.45 percent.</p>
